      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pre-tbl-vlt-000      thru pre-tbl-vlt-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su stato di uscita                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-vlt-tbl-flg        =    spaces
                     go to pre-exe-pgm-200.
